Prince Thiza of KwaDlamahlahla had suffered a short illness. PIETERMARITZBURG - Another senior member of the AmaZulu Royal Family has passed. Prince Thiza of KwaDlamahlahla had suffered a short illness. READ: AmaZulu Royal Family vows to go ahead with coronation He was very close to the late King Goodwill Zwelithini KaBhekuzulu, who passed away in March. Queen Mantfombi Dlamini followed a few weeks later. Prince Thiza's death comes as the royal family prepares for the coronation of King Misuzulu KaZwelithini.